<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Results - Government College of Engineering, Jalgaon</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        .header {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 15px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        .header .emblem {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            position: absolute;
            right: 15px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }

        .header .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1d3557;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background-color: #1d3557;
            padding: 15px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: #f1faee;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            color: #a8dadc;
        }

        /* Main Content Styles */
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #1d3557;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .introduction {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Key Features Section */
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .feature {
            background-color: #e8f5ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            flex: 1;
            margin: 0 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .feature h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1d3557;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature p {
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Login Section */
        .login-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 50px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .login-option {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .login-option img {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #e63946;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f1faee;
            color: #e63946;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Notice Board */
        .notice-board {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .notice-board h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #e63946;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .notice {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #1d3557;
        }

        .contact p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background-color: #1d3557;
            color: #f1faee;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Header with Logo, Title, and Emblem -->
<header class="header">
    <img src="/images/collegelogo.png" alt="College Logo" class="logo">
    <div>
        <h1 class="title">Government College of Engineering, Jalgaon</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">(An Autonomous Institute of Government of Maharashtra)</p>
    </div>
    <img src="/images/rajmudralogo.png" alt="Emblem" class="emblem">
</header>

<!-- Navbar -->
<nav class="navbar">
    <a class="nav-link" href="/teacher/signup">Teacher Signup</a>
</nav>

<div class="content">
    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="introduction">
        <h2 class="section-title">Welcome to the Student Result Management System</h2>
        <p>Our result management platform is designed to provide students with easy and secure access to their academic results. This initiative is powered by the Government College of Engineering, Jalgaon, with a focus on transparency and convenience.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Secure Access</h3>
            <p>Only authorized students and teachers can access the system, ensuring the security of your academic records.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Real-time Updates</h3>
            <p>Get the latest updates on results and other academic notifications in real-time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Easy Navigation</h3>
            <p>The user-friendly interface makes it simple for students to view and download their results.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Login Section -->
    <section class="login-container">
        <div class="login-option">
            <img src="/images/teacher-icon.png" alt="Teacher Logo">
            <a href="/teacher/login" class="btn">Teacher Login</a>
        </div>
        <div class="login-option">
            <img src="/images/student-icon.jpg" alt="Student Logo">
            <a href="/student/login" class="btn">Student Login</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Notice Board Section -->
    <section class="notice-board">
        <h3>Notice Board</h3>
        <div class="notice">1. Results for the semester exams will be released on 15th Nov.</div>
        <div class="notice">2. Revaluation forms are now available. Submit by 10th Nov.</div>
        <div class="notice">3. The next semester starts on 1st Dec. Be prepared!</div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="contact">
        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions or require assistance, please contact the academic office at (0257) 2258414 or email support@gcoej.ac.in</p>
    </section>
    <!-- Footer -->
<footer class="footer">
    &copy; 2024 Government College of Engineering, Jalgaon. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>